====== inet-4.x ======

2017-09-21  Zoltan Bojthe

	All: Merged InterfaceEntry and corresponding NIC module.

	  - InterfaceEntry->getName() replaced to
	InterfaceEntry->getInterfaceName()

2017-07-12  Levente Mészáros

	All: Renamed NotifierConsts files to Simsignals.

2017-07-12  Levente Mészáros

	All: Renamed NF_PACKET_DROP to packetDrop(Signal).

2017-07-12  Levente Mészáros

	All: Replaced remaining packet drop signals with the generic one.

2017-02-03  Levente Mészáros

	All: Renamed to INetworkHeader.

2017-01-23  Levente Mészáros

	All: Updated all affected protocols to use the new bit or byte units.

2017-01-19  Levente Mészáros

	Link: Renamed MACFrameBase to MacHeaderBase.

2017-01-25  Zoltan Bojthe

	CSMA: Changed to use the new Packet class.

2016-10-26  Zoltan Bojthe

	refactoring: removed compatibility macros required for OMNeT++ 4.x builds
	+ warning fixes

2016-05-02  Levente Mészáros

	Link: Changed registerInterface calls to use the gate of the NIC module
	if possible.

	This simplifies interface registration process for compound mac modules.

2016-05-02  Levente Mészáros

	Link: Added new registerInterface() calls.

2015-06-23  Levente Mészáros

	Link: Added network protocol to BMac, LMac, CSMA frames.

